<div id="content" class="column span-16">
<h1>MASiVE</h1>
<h2>Algorithm</h2>
<p>
MASiVe is an expertly-built tool for the large-scale, yet sensitive and highly accurate, discovery, preliminary analysis, and insertion age estimation of intact Sirevirus LTR-retrotransposons in plant genomic sequences. 
Validation was based on the recently available and annotated large maize chromosome one. Results show a considerable improvement in the annotation of Sireviruses, and support our approach as an important addition 
to the bioinformatics toolbox of plant biologists.
</br></br>
Availability: PERL source code and essential files are available on the sidebar. The freely available Vmatch, LTRharvest, Wise2, and MAFFT algorithms are required.
</br></br>
Funding: This work was supported by the FP6 Biosapiens Network of Excellence (contract number LSHG-CT-2003-503265).
</br></br>
</p>
<h2>Data</h2>
<p>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1.MASiVE.fulllength.OK.fasta.gz" target="_blank">10,619</a> [gzipped, 17MB] FASTA-formatted sequences of full-length / intact Sireviruses in the ten chromosomes of the 1st version of the maize B73 genome
</br></br>
GFF-formatted coordinates of the above, split into chromosomes: 
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr1.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">1</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr2.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">2</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr3.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">3</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr4.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">4</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr5.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">5</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr6.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">6</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr7.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">7</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr8.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">8</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr9.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">9</a>
<a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/ZmB73_AGPv1_chr10.MASiVE.gff" target="_blank">10</a>
</br></br>
a Sirevirus- and monocot-specific hidden Markov <a href="http://bat.ina.certh.gr/tools/masive/downloads/Sirevirus_ENVmonocot-mod-hmmls.hmm" target="_blank">model</a> (HMM) of the <i>ENV</i> (envelope) gene
</p>
